strings.suggest.checklist.brief: Qala uhlu lokuhlola ukusebenza: qinisekisa ukuthi amathuluzi abalulekile afakiwe futhi ukwakhiwa kuyasebenza.
strings.suggest.checklist.extensive: Uhlu lokuhlola ukusebenza okuphezulu: gxila ezinyathelweni ezithuthukisa isivinini nokusebenza kahle.
strings.suggest.memory.low: Imemori yamahhala ephansi: vala izinhlelo zokusebenza ezingasetshenzisiwe noma qala kabusha ukuze ukhulule i-RAM.
strings.suggest.memory.veryHigh: Ukusetshenziswa kwe-RAM >= 90%: vala izinhlelo zokusebenza ezinzima, misa kancane ukwakha, noma ukhuphule i-RAM yesistimu.
strings.suggest.memory.high: Ukusetshenziswa kwe-RAM >= 80%: cabanga ukuvala izinhlelo zokusebenza noma ukukhulisa i-RAM uma lokhu kuvamile.
strings.suggest.memory.reserve: Gcina i-RAM yamahhala engu-20% yenqolobane nemisebenzi OS; U-10% ubuncane bokugwema ukwehla.
strings.suggest.cpu.high: Umthwalo CPU ophezulu: hlola Isiphathi Somsebenzi ukuthola izinqubo ezinzima.
strings.suggest.internet.failed: Ukuhlola i-inthanethi kwehlulekile: qinisekisa uxhumano lwakho noma i-firewall.
strings.suggest.internet.latency: Ukubambezeleka kwe-inthanethi okuphezulu: zama ukushintsha amanethiwekhi noma ukuqalisa kabusha umzila.
strings.suggest.os.updates: macOS izibuyekezo ziyatholakala: faka izibuyekezo zakamuva.
strings.suggest.gpu.full: Qalisa ukuxilonga okugcwele ukuze ufake GPU kanye nemininingwane yokucubungula.
strings.suggest.ide.cap: JetBrains IDE ikhephu itholiwe: khulisa IDE usayizi wenqwaba uma ukusebenza kuhamba kancane.
strings.suggest.wifi.weak: Isignali Wi-Fi ebuthaka (<60%): sondela kumzila noma shintshela ku-Ethernet.
strings.suggest.wifi.weakRssi: Isignali ye-Wi-Fi ebuthaka (i-RSSI ephansi): sondela kumzila noma shintshela ku-Ethernet.
strings.suggest.power.plan: Uhlelo lwamandla alusethelwe ekusebenzeni okuphezulu: shintshela kokuthi Ukusebenza Okungcono Kakhulu/okuPhezulu ngenkathi ubhala ikhodi noma wakha.
strings.suggest.vscode.extensions: VS Code: khubaza izandiso ezingasetshenzisiwe futhi ukhiphe amafolda okwakha/okukhiphayo ekubukeni kwefayela nasekuseshweni.
strings.suggest.jetbrains.tune: JetBrains IDEs: khubaza ama-plugin angasetshenzisiwe, ungafaki okukhiphayo kokwakha kusukela kunkomba, futhi ukhuphule usayizi wenqwaba uma kudingeka.
strings.suggest.vs.parallel: Visual Studio: vumela ukwakhiwa kwephrojekthi efanayo futhi ukhiphe amaphrojekthi angasetshenzisiwe ukuze unciphise isikhathi sokulayisha isixazululo.
strings.suggest.xcode.derived: Xcode: hlanza i-DerivedData uma ukhomba noma izikhathi zokwakha zikhuphuka.
strings.suggest.android.accel: Android Studio: vumela ihadiwe yokulingisa isheshise futhi ugcine Gradle inqolobane kusitoreji esisheshayo.
strings.suggest.node.lts: Node.js: sebenzisa ukukhishwa kwakamuva kwe-LTS futhi ugcine ukuncika kwephrojekthi kusitoreji se-SSD.
strings.suggest.ts.incremental: TypeScript: nika amandla ukwakha okukhuphukayo noma izinkomba zephrojekthi kumakhodi amakhulu.
strings.suggest.python.venv: I-Python: sebenzisa izindawo ezibonakalayo ukuze ugcine ukufakwa kuhlukanisiwe futhi kuyashesha.
strings.suggest.java.lts: I-Java: sebenzisa i-LTS JDK yamanje futhi unike amandla izinqolobane zokwakha (Gradle/Maven) ukuze kwakhiwe kabusha ngokushesha.
strings.suggest.docker.windows: Docker Ideskithophu (IWindows): sebenzisa i-WSL2 backend bese ushuna CPU/RAM imikhawulo yomthwalo wakho wokusebenza.
strings.suggest.docker.mac: Docker Ideskithophu (macOS): shuna CPU/RAM imikhawulo kanye nokwabelana ngefayela (VirtioFS uma ikhona).
strings.checklist.osDrivers: Buyekeza OS nezishayeli zedivayisi (GPU, chipset, Wi-Fi/LAN) kuzinguqulo ezizinzile zakamuva.
strings.checklist.powerPlan: Sebenzisa uhlelo lwamandla Okusebenza Okuphezulu/Okuhle Kakhulu ngenkathi ubhala ikhodi noma wakha.
strings.checklist.startupApps: Khubaza noma nquma izinhlelo zokusebenza zokuqalisa namasevisi angemuva ongawasebenzisi.
strings.checklist.diskSpace: Gcina okungenani i-20% yesikhala samahhala sediski; sebenzisa ukuhlanzwa kwediski futhi ususe amafayela amakhulu wesikhashana.
strings.checklist.ssd: Khetha isitoreji se-SSD samaphrojekthi; gwema ukwakha okusindayo kumadrayivu angaphandle ahamba kancane.
strings.checklist.antivirus: Ungafaki amafolda ephrojekthi (ama-node_modules, build, dist) ekuskeneni kwe-antivirus ngesikhathi sangempela.
strings.checklist.wifi: Sebenzisa i-Ethernet noma eqinile 5GHz Wi-Fi; buyekeza i-router firmware futhi uqalise kabusha ngezikhathi ezithile.
strings.checklist.dns: Misa i-DNS kumhlinzeki osheshayo futhi uqinisekise ukubambezeleka okuphansi kokulandwa kwephakheji.
strings.checklist.browser: Khawulela amathebhu esiphequluli futhi uvale izinhlelo zokusebenza ezinzima ngesikhathi sokwakha.
strings.checklist.hwAccel: Nika amandla ukusheshisa kwehadiwe lapho kusekelwa khona (isiphequluli/IDE).
strings.checklist.cliTools: Gcina amathuluzi angu-CLI esesikhathini samanje (Node.js, npm, Git, Docker, Java).
strings.checklist.reboot: Qalisa kabusha ngemva kwezibuyekezo ezinkulu ukuze usule izinqubo zakudala nezingidi.
